OL,6,FMr McLarnon said he suffered from
OL,7,Fdepression and trauma due to his
OL,8,Fexperiences on the day of the bombing.
OL,10,FHe said: "I could not walk up Market
OL,11,FStreet, even after it re-opened and I
OL,12,Favoided the town centre.
OL,14,F"I would have nightmares about what I
OL,15,Fhad seen and I felt useless, guilt,
OL,16,Fanger and depressed about my inability
OL,17,Fto help anyone on the day of the bomb.
OL,19,F"I was angry with the bombers and that
OL,20,Fthey have evaded justice.
